data.description: This 2 bedroom, 1 bath ranch home is nestled on a large lot with an oversized 2 stall heated and cooled garage! Inside the home you will find a large living room, a kitchen with lots of cabinets, and a sunroom area.  Outside is a 2 stall oversized garage complete with heating and cooling and a large flat yard to enjoy outdoor activities.  Don't miss out on this amazing home tucked in a quiet neighborhood only minutes to East Peoria or downtown Peoria. Come and take a look today!
